description: Joey Baltimore is fresh out of massage therapy school, but unfortunately, his first client is a little testy. Rod Daily is just a bit cranky due to some tension in his butt and groin area, and he's hoping Joey has what it takes to work it out. Luckily for him, Joey specialized in this region at school, so he knows that all it takes make someone less testy is to satisfy the testes.Enjoy!
title: Rod Massage
